job.title: India Navy SSC Electrical Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 40 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:40

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Electrical branch for course JAN 2022

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for engineers have been published by the Indian Navy for electrician vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of an electrician, from 16-07-2021, and till 30-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for an electrician in the Indian Navy, your BE/B.Tech must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 16-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 30-07-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

India Navy electrician Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for India Navy SSC Electrical Recruitment 2021? 

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the electrician. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of India Navy and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by the Indian Navy 
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
